      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a reference framework for Operations, Administration, and Maintenance (OAM) in Transparent Interconnection of Lots of Links (TRILL) networks.  The focus of the document is on the fault and performance management aspects of TRILL OAM.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
